<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Analog Society - Knowledge Preservation & Material Exchange</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Join a community of makers, collectors, and enthusiasts preserving analog knowledge through documentation, trading, and critical discourse.">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="/scripts/offline-storage.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main>
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Preserve • Document • Exchange</h2>
                    <p class="lead">Join a global community of makers, collectors, and enthusiasts who value the enduring beauty and craftsmanship of analog materials. Document your collection, trade with peers, and preserve physical knowledge for future generations.</p>
                    <div class="image-container"> 
                        <img 
                            src="images/portalto80s.jpeg" 
                            alt="Vintage analog equipment representing the beauty of physical materials" 
                            class="hero-image"
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <a href="/auth/sign-up" class="btn" aria-label="Join the Community">Join the Community</a>
                        <a href="/items" class="btn btn-secondary" aria-label="Browse Collections">Browse Collections</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="special-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h3>Critical Discourse</h3>
                    <p>Engage in thoughtful discussions about technology, institutions, and the importance of analog alternatives in our increasingly digital world. Share insights, challenge assumptions, and explore the intersection of analog and digital cultures.</p>
                    <a href="/critique" class="btn btn-secondary" aria-label="Join the Discussion">Join the Discussion</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="special-section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
                <div class="container">
                    <h3>Trading Hub</h3>
                    <p>Exchange, trade, rent, and share analog materials with trusted community members. Build lasting connections through material exchange while preserving knowledge through collaborative sharing.</p>
                    <a href="/trading" class="btn" aria-label="Start Trading">Start Trading</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="special-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h3>Why Choose Analog Society?</h3>
                    <p>Discover the personal and community benefits of documenting your analog materials. Build a comprehensive digital inventory, track collection value, and contribute to global knowledge preservation while maintaining full data ownership.</p>
                    <a href="/benefits" class="btn btn-secondary" aria-label="Explore Benefits">Explore Benefits</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>